text:
Announcement: we’re hosting the first ever “CFP office hours” this Saturday 3/20, 4pm UTC.

If you have questions about the JuliaCon CFP or if are not sure if you should submit a proposal, come to this event and we’ll answer all your questions.

<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ou03SfY8lNo>
